### Negative Scenarios

#### TC_02: {Test Case Name}
- **Type**: Negative
- **Description**: {detailed_description}
- **Feature File**: `src/test/java/com/Bizom/{SuiteName}/feature/{feature_file}.feature`
- **Payload**: {payload_file_name}
- **Expected Status**: {status_code}
- **Validation Points**:
  - Status Code: {expected_status}
  - Error Fields: {error_field_validations}
  - Performance: < {time_limit}ms
- **Business Logic**: {error_condition_validation}
- **Tags**: @{ModuleName} @NegativeScenario @Sanity

